{"tid":2506513,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉拳打妻男友人 柳俊江獲撤控","createTime":"2021-04-27T11:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T14:34:28.000Z","uid":171506,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d8bf02fef7a133c49b67808c8dae6f14df3086e2","tid":2506513,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:03:39.000Z","msg":"傳媒人柳俊江涉去年9月與妻子男友人打鬥，被控以一項「襲擊致造成實際身體傷害」罪，案件今日於觀塘裁判法院再提堂，柳俊江獲控方撤銷控罪，獲判守行為12個月，簽1000元守行為，兼付500元堂費。<br />\n<br />\n柳俊江在庭上同意案情，指當時正與妻子進行離婚手續，案發當日晚上7時許，柳妻與事主在涉案餐廳吃晚飯，柳俊江到餐廳對質，拳打並推事主多次，柳表示對方先動手，事主驗傷確認鼻樑有瘀傷、上唇有擦傷。<br />\n<br />\n40歲被告柳俊江報稱商人，被控於2020年9月9日，在觀塘亞金南洋茶室襲擊男子儲孝和，並對該男子造成身體傷害。"},{"pid":"71c162732bfa48a1687e547cc3741f5cafe430a2","tid":2506513,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:04:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2780084/%E6%B6%89%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93%E5%A6%BB%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%8B%E4%BA%BA+%E6%9F%B3%E4%BF%8A%E6%B1%9F%E7%8D%B2%E6%92%A4%E6%8E%A7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2780084%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%258B%25B3%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25A6%25BB%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%258F%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%2B%25E6%259F%25B3%25E4%25BF%258A%25E6%25B1%259F%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2592%25A4%25E6%258E%25A7&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oG7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=5864c911\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2780084/%E6%B6%89%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93%E5%A6%BB%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%8B%E4%BA%BA+%E6%9F%B3%E4%BF%8A%E6%B1%9F%E7%8D%B2%E6%92%A4%E6%8E%A7</a>"},{"pid":"ba2cb7b1305ec245c7e201c11f34535940f6b03f","tid":2506513,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:04:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"902d5bb148a9442d917708766066efe29f09662f","tid":2506513,"uid":307927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco